13:51.497 --> 13:53.266 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: How come?

13:53.299 --> 14:00.440 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN O'LEARY: First of all, I
