14:42.548 --> 14:44.417 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: He also
mentioned immigration.

14:44.450 --> 14:48.321 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SCULLY: Where people can
come from Greece,
where youth unemployment is 50
percent, to

14:48.354 --> 14:54.327 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
London on the hope of a job,
whereas if you
have got a skilled worker,
skilled I.T. consultant

14:54.360 --> 14:59.298 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
