bureaucracy
to have the hope of coming here
to do a job

15:04.303 --> 15:05.972 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that we really want them to do.

15:06.005 --> 15:07.874 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And, finally,
