Justice series.

18:26.906 --> 18:31.610 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: This facility
in the rural
town of Moose Lake is where
Minnesota puts

18:31.644 --> 18:36.415 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
