19:25.097 --> 19:29.435 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CRAIG BOLTE: I have been in for
about 10 years
now. All in all, I have been
locked up for

19:29.468 --> 19:31.437 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
