19:31.470 --> 19:38.344 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The "PBS
NewsHour" was granted
rare access to Minnesota's sex
offender program.

19:38.377 --> 19:43.115 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We could film interviews inside
this one room,
but, almost everywhere else, we
could only

19:43.149 --> 19:48.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
