19:54.527 --> 19:58.064 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And that concern is why
legislatures in 20
states have set up programs like
this to hold

19:58.097 --> 20:03.235 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
