being held for
years past their sentences.

20:07.073 --> 20:11.310 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ERIC JANUS, Mitchell Hamline
School of Law:
It's outrageous. That's one of
the more outrageous

20:11.343 --> 20:13.179 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
