20:13.212 --> 20:16.715 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Eric Janus is
a law professor
and longtime critic of
Minnesota's sex offender

20:16.749 --> 20:22.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
