capture that.

43:00.244 --> 43:04.148 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes. So, how did
you approach
it? What was different about
doing something

43:04.182 --> 43:05.983 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
