43:06.017 --> 43:09.086 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: Oh. Well, the
big thing is,
you spend -- probably you want
the book to

43:09.120 --> 43:13.858 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
