and about
30 percent for the adult reading
to the kid.

43:13.891 --> 43:15.827 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Because you have
the parent
in mind.

43:15.860 --> 43:17.161 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: Exactly. You
have to.

43:17.195 --> 43:18.429 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Yes. Thank you, I
guess all
parents are saying.

43:18.463 --> 43:20.231 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: Yes. You have
to.

43:20.264 --> 43:24.802 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So -- and that balance is really
difficult,
finding that balance, where you
make the book

43:24.836 --> 43:27.872 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
