43:29.774 --> 43:35.980 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: This book ended
up being -- I
tried to get the intellectual
idea in place

43:36.013 --> 43:39.851 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
