43:56.801 --> 43:58.469 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Wow.

43:58.503 --> 44:03.241 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: And it had never
occurred
to me. The existential weight of
being named

44:03.274 --> 44:07.211 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
