Thunder Boy, right?

44:37.408 --> 44:38.709 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: Yes.

44:38.743 --> 44:40.111 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And trying to
figure out who
he is, in a sense.

44:40.144 --> 44:43.114 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: This idea of the
kid in search
of his own identity.

44:43.147 --> 44:46.918 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This is a loving, supportive
Native American
family. And I thought that was
important to

44:46.951 --> 44:48.719 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
show as well.

44:48.753 --> 44:51.188 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And he goes
through all his
experiences and says, maybe I
should be named

44:51.222 --> 44:52.957 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
