Toys Are Awesome.

45:09.240 --> 45:11.008 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

45:11.042 --> 45:14.545 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHERMAN ALEXIE: So he's a kid.
He's a Native
American kid. He's both at the
same time.

45:14.579 --> 45:18.316 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: How important is
